      "description": "Calling all restoration fans and DIY mechanics! This vehicle is the ultimate project car, offering a fantastic opportunity for someone ready to bring a classic back to its former glory. While it currently requires significant mechanical and cosmetic work, it serves as a great foundation for a full rebuild or a dedicated parts car. Grab this chance to start your next big automotive adventure at a price that leaves plenty of room for your upgrades!",
