    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, featuring a flawless exterior finish and an interior that retains its original factory integrity. Every mechanical component has been rigorously inspected to ensure peak performance, offering a driving experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade vehicle of unparalleled quality and provenance.",
      "price": 43900.0,
