    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I am parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she's a total beauty! This car is in incredible, showroom-quality shape\u2014it's been garage-kept, meticulously detailed, and looks just as gorgeous as the day I got it. If you're looking for that 'fresh off the lot' feel and a ride that's been loved every mile, you've found it! I'm happy to chat and answer any questions you have. Let's get you behind the wheel of this gem!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
